 en Ren\u00e9 Karst.","category":"Spelshow, Komedie"},"74637":{"channel":"22","start":"1627500600","end":"1627502400","first":"other","idtitle":"112VANDAAG","title":"112 Vandaag","program_id":"877481877","date":"","icon":"https:\/\/images.tv.kpn.com\/epg\/5A9BByIb1K07KEha8l35gSErdsxsDWFq6wwbBwPbxLSA\/1920x1080.jpg?blurred=false","description":"Liveprogramma over de meest opvallende meldingen en calamiteiten die in de afgelopen 24 uur bij het nationale noodnummer zijn binnengekomen.","category":"Reality"},"74638":{"channel":"22","start":"1627502400","end":"1627506000","first":"D","idtitle":"DEALARMCENTRALEPECHONDERWEG","title":"De Alarmcentrale: Pech Onderweg","program_id":"877481880","date":"2021","icon":"https:\/\/images.tv.kpn.com\/epg\/1r5hYCYeX3GV9BVlj0fLfvkxqNsgvoTHRwvoJwDLW6Nw\/1920x1080.jpg?blurred=false","description":"Realityserie waarin Jochem van Gelder Nederlandse hulpverleners volgt die automobilisten helpen die met pech langs de weg zijn beland.","category":"Reality"},"74639":{"channel":"22","start":"1627506000","end":"1627509600","first":"other","idtitle":"24UURINDEER","title":"24 Uur In De E.R.","program_id":"877481883","date":"2018","icon":"https:\/\/images.tv.kpn.com\/epg\/aHIQpTvOx5Ofrbcv1P9C9CWyQKx0ouzR9CUFk9A9A4bNsq1Q\/1920x1080.jpg?blurred=false","description":"Britse medische realityserie over de eerstehulpafdeling van St. George's Hospital in Zuid-Londen, een van de grootste ziekenhuizen van Groot-Brittanni\u00eb.","category":"Reality, Medisch"}}